Sentencas: The lack of accurate modeling of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC's) and their systems has resulted in limitations in identifying key operating parameters and allowing for system configuration.
Titulo: Electrochemical and thermal simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The purpose of this study is to address each level of modeling needed to identify key parameters as well as integrating each level of modeling.
Titulo: Electrochemical and thermal simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The first level deals with the single cell and its electrochemical and thermal issues.
Titulo: Electrochemical and thermal simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The second level deals with the bundling of cells to form an SOFC stack while the third level incorporates the slack results into an overall thermal system.
Titulo: Electrochemical and thermal simulation of a solid oxide fuel cell
